==English==

===Etymology===
From {{Turk.}} [[abdest#Turkish|abdest]] < {{Pers.}} {{fa-Arab|[[آبدست]]}} (ābdast) < compound of {{fa-Arab|[[آب]]}} (āb) '''water''' + {{fa-Arab|[[دست]]}} (dast) '''hand'''.

===Noun===
'''abdest'''

# [[Islam]]ic act of washing parts of the body using [[water]] for ritual [[prayer]]s and for handling and reading the [[Qur'an]].

